{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 31,
  "title": "第三十一章（貴左）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "夫兵者，不祥之器也。物或惡之。故有欲者，弗居。"
    },
    {
      "text": "君子居則貴左，用兵則貴右。故兵者，非君子之器也。兵者，不祥之器也。不得已而用之。銛龐為上。"
    },
    {
      "text": "勿美也。若美之，是樂殺人也。夫樂殺人，不可以得志於天下矣。是以吉事上左，喪事上右。是以偏將軍居左，上將軍居右。言以喪禮居之也。"
    },
    {
      "text": "殺人眾，以悲依立之。戰勝，以喪禮處之。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 23,
          "end": 23
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "佳，飾也。祥，善也。兵者，驚精神，濁和氣，不善人之器也，不當修飾之。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 11,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "兵動則有所害，故萬物無有不惡之者。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 23,
          "end": 23
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "有道之人不處其國。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 10,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "貴柔弱也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 17,
          "end": 18
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "貴剛強也，此言兵道與君子之道反，所貴者異也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 1,
          "end": 2
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "兵，革者。不善之器也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 19,
          "end": 20
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "非君子所貴重之器也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 37,
          "end": 38
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "謂遭衰逆亂禍，欲加萬民，乃用之以自守。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 45,
          "end": 45
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不貪土地，利人財寶。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 45,
          "end": 45
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "雖得勝而不以為利己也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 14
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "美得勝者，是為喜樂殺人者也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 14,
          "end": 29
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "為人君而樂殺人者，此不可使得志於天下矣，為人主必專制人命，妄行刑誅。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 26,
          "end": 27
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "左，生位也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-14",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 29,
          "end": 41
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "陰道殺人。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-15",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 35,
          "end": 36
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "偏將軍卑而居陽者，以其不專殺也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-16",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 41,
          "end": 42
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "上將軍尊而居陰者，以其專主殺也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-17",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 48,
          "end": 49
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "上將軍居右，喪禮尚右，死人貴陰也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-18",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 63,
          "end": 63
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "傷己德薄，不能以道化人，而害無辜之民。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-19",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 51,
          "end": 52
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "古者戰勝，將軍居喪主禮之位，素服而哭之，明君子貴德而賤兵，不得以而誅不祥，心不樂之，比於喪也，知後世用兵不已故悲痛之。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
